title: BRIEF-Snap-On Inc says ‍On Feb 20 Co Entered Into Underwriting Agreement
text: February 26, 2018 / 4:17 PM / Updated 2 minutes ago BRIEF-Snap-On Inc says ‍On Feb 20 Co Entered Into Underwriting Agreement Reuters Staff Feb 26 (Reuters) - Snap-On Inc: * SNAP-ON INC - ‍ON FEBRUARY 20, 2018, CO ENTERED INTO AN UNDERWRITING AGREEMENT - SEC FILING​ * SNAP-ON INC - ‍PURSUANT TO AGREEMENT CO AGREED TO SELL AND UNDERWRITERS AGREED TO PURCHASE, $400 MILLION PRINCIPAL AMOUNT OF CO‘S 4.100% NOTES DUE 2048​ * SNAP-ON INC - ‍NOTES WILL MATURE ON MARCH 1, 2048​ Source text - ( bit.ly/2FwZ4xo ) Further company coverage:
